Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:35.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,友加里 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:40.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你从刚刚开始都在干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:42.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:43.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:45.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:50.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我好像看到早苗在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:51.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,友加里有看到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:53.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  我没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:09:00.43,Takagi san—Picture 02-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1484,324)}{\fad(450,450)}随身物品检查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:06.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,说起来 今天好像要检查随身物品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:09.11,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.91,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦  你一点都不慌嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我又没有带什么不能带的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你确定？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你这么一问  我还真不敢确定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:24.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,万一我一不留神把漫画或者游戏带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:29.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,都怪高木同学  我越来越慌了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那我们就预演一下随身物品检查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:36.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这有什么意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:39.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,现在确认一遍  真要检查的时候不就放心了么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:44.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么开始检查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:53.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不由得紧张起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:56.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没有问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:09:58.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:01.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,对老师要用敬语
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:03.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,完全进入老师的角色了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:04.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:05.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:10.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊  这是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:13.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么了  发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:14.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我带了什么不该带的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:19.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我以为是什么  原来只是教科书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:20.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:21.82,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,吓了一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:25.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没有被吓到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:31.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我才没有被您吓到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:33.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:36.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那这回轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:43.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:44.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,让我吓一吓高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:53.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,嗯什么的  西片心目中的大人形象挺有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:54.48,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:57.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要对老师使用敬语
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:58.70,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:02.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学这家伙  现在老师可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:10.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,一副从容的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:13.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看来她什么违禁物品都没带
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那我只能虚张声势一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:21.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,运动服好像鼓鼓的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:26.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,难道说  她从容的表情是装的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:28.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,老师怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:30.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,试着套一下她的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:34.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你的运动服里是不是藏了东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:35.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,您可以检查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.08,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,来  您请您请
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:47.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,咦  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:51.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,太羞耻了  我怎么可能碰她的运动服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:52.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,5…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:54.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,4…3…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:56.14,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:56.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,2…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:11:58.22,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,1…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:01.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,0 时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:03.86,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,为什么定规则的是高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:06.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,明明我才是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.23,0:12:07.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不过今天不用检查随身物品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:10.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:12.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我只是觉得可能会有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:16.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,只是在捉弄我而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:18.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:23.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,给  谢谢你借我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:24.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:28.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片老师太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:37.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你可以随时检查我的随身物品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:40.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:44.36,Takagi san—Picture 02-3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(448,406)}图书委员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:46.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那么…文化祭委员就
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:48.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,木村和月本来当
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:50.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,图书委员…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:53.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,书的背面装有借书卡对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:57.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,拿出卡片让学生填上名字和日期
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:59.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,然后收好卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:02.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,书还回来了就写上归还日期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:03.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,再将卡片放回书中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:06.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,大概就是这样  很简单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:09.76,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就这样  虽然应该没多少人来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:11.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但要认真干哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:18.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,以后咱每周都有一天不能午休了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:19.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没什么不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:21.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看看书的话很快就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:24.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:25.79,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,读起来很有趣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:27.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学经常读书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:30.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,跟看漫画五五开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片看起来不太读书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:36.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我也读的啊  时不时的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:40.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,反正挺闲的  我去拿点书来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:48.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,书么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:55.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,提不起什么兴趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:58.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有没有什么想看的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:05.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,恐龙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:08.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,图鉴真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.15,0:14:10.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,找到什么好书了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:13.00,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:14.97,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:17.52,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她绝对会觉得我看图鉴很幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.59,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我说  我想了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:23.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要不要交换两人找到的书来看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:25.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,诶？可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:26.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那就定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:43.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我没看过这本书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:44.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,讲什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:48.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我也不清楚  随便选的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:52.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,恐龙图鉴？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:56.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看你饶有兴致地在读这本书
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:58.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还是被发现了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.25,Takagi san—Picture 02-4,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.43\an1\fscx90\fscy98\\pos(436,428)\fad(600,0)}勒苏维斯龙 \N剑龙目草食性恐龙 \N栖息在中生代侏罗纪的欧洲\N 跟剑龙是同类 \N除了背部及尾部的骨板和针刺外\N 肩部也生长着尖刺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\p1\an8\1a&H5f\4a&Hff\3a&Hff\2a&Hff\fscx147\fscy160\frz29.43\pos(629.467,348.133)\fad(600,0)}m 0 0 l 0 -174 l 296 -174 l 299 1
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.25,Takagi san—Picture 02-4,,0,0,0,,{\an1\frz29.43\pos(1092,676)\fscx90\fscy98\fad(600,0)}无鼻角龙\N 角龙科恐龙 \N栖息在白垩纪末期的加拿大 \N被发现的仅有头骨的化石 \N与其它角龙相比鼻子及面部更小\N 人们推测其为三角龙的祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\p1\an8\1a&H5f\4a&Hff\3a&Hff\2a&Hff\fscx147\fscy160\frz29.43\\pos(1290,592)\fad(600,0)}m 0 0 l 0 -174 l 296 -174 l 299 1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:15.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学看书的样子真适合她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:19.19,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你在看我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:24.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哦  我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:26.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,难得有机会两人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:29.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你在伺机把平日被我捉弄的份报复回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:36.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,差不多是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:39.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:42.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:46.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,诶  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:47.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,「听八乙女如是说道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,田中的果汁掉落在地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:52.28,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,操场响彻着棒球部成员们的嘶喊…」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:52.29,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}在朗诵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:55.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.80,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,结果一个人都没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:06.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,下周也这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:09.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:14.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,下周西片也读点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:18.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,有什么推荐的书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:21.43,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:24.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,除了今天西片给我的书
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:25.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,全部都可以推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:28.07,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,什么  那本书有那么糟糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:30.34,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没有  很有意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:32.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,只是不推荐西片读
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:34.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,几个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:38.09,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为会暴露书里没有那句话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:40.55,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,诶  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:42.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:44.31,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不对吧  你刚才说了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:46.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学？啥情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:50.36,Takagi san—Picture 02-5,,0,0,0,,{\frz269.7\pos(150,362)}夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.19,0:16:56.24,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.05,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学  你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:01.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,跑腿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:02.21,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:03.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我在跑步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:04.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:06.58,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你经常跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:08.95,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也就偶尔跑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:11.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,之前为了备战马拉松大赛而跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:13.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,结果还上瘾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:15.78,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你还练过这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:17.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,虽然输给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:18.18,Takagi san—Picture 02-6,,0,0,0,,{\frz4.675\fad(300,450)\move(1024,344,1024,358,0,1650)}女生折返
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:20.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.30,0:17:22.53,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,下次我会赢你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:26.74,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那你要跑多远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:30.15,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还挺看心情的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:32.18,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,跑累了就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:34.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,上次都跑到那头的海边了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:35.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那头？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:40.66,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学难得在佩服我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:42.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这下我得…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:43.27,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:44.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,当然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.13,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,那还相当远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:48.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,你说的是真话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:50.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,绝对是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:55.06,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,算了  那你加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:57.09,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:59.55,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她肯定没相信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:02.61,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,行  现在我就跑到海边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:04.50,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,拍照为证发给她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:07.51,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:10.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我要让你承认我的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:14.75,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:29.20,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,本来遇到高木同学时就打算回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:30.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,体力不够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:36.09,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:38.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,要放弃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.64,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不  我要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.28,0:18:45.40,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,只要到了海边…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:47.85,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,哇  西片好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:49.33,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我再也不会捉弄你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.56,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她就会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:58.10,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,等着瞧吧  高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:04.83,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:18.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,满满的成就感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:20.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不对  不是想这个的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:22.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,得赶紧给高木同学发照片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:25.39,Takagi san—Picture 02-7,,0,0,0,,{\frz12.75\move(860,136,874,188,0,1943)}{\fs40\t(0,2000,\fs35)}高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:24.64,Takagi san—Picture 02-8,,0,0,0,,{\frz12.75\move(1024,250,1026,280,0,1150)}{\fs40\t(0,2000,\fs35)}为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:24.60,Takagi san—Picture 02-8,,0,0,0,,{\frz12.75\move(1110,586,1102,582,24,1150)}{\fs40\t(0,2000,\fs35)}我到海边了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:25.39,Takagi san—Picture 02-8,,0,0,0,,{\frz12.75\move(1090,522,1024,304,0,250,)}我到海边了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:25.46,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,选中发送
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:27.68,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:29.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好好领教我的厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:32.69,Takagi san—Picture 02-8,,0,0,0,,{\an1\frz12.55\move(740,420,736,478,0,750)}夕阳好美啊。谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:39.54,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,重点不是那个啊  是海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:40.26,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,这下不就变成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:43.12,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我只是在分享夕阳给高木同学看而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:43.99,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.94,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,高木同学  你怎么在这
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:55.63,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,真是不错的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:59.84,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,跑完腿后骑车飞奔过来也值了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:01.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:07.41,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:20.88,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我猜你会不会为了给我看证据
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:23.04,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,就一路跑到海边来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:24.96,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:28.42,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我又被耍了个团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:31.25,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不过我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:34.65,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,因为西片为了给我发夕阳的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:37.23,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,努力跑过来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:40.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是这样  但又不是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:42.77,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,红通通的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:45.71,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:46.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.38,0:20:50.32,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:53.16,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不过西片的脸更红
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:57.45,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可恶  我只是想让她觉得我了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:59.67,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,仅仅是在为这个努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:03.93,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,追在西片身后真是值了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.63,0:21:09.72,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,能和西片一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:11.38,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,看夕阳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:16.73,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:26.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不不  她在说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.81,0:21:28.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,她来只是为了捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.35,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,可不能被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.42,0:21:31.17,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:34.37,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,还有一丝心动的我真是太蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:38.44,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,不过话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:40.01,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片真厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:42.47,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,竟然真的能跑到海边来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:55.49,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,也没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.77,0:21:58.90,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,西片  被我夸了在偷笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:00.36,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,我可没偷笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.73,0:22:02.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,虽然达成了目的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:02.60,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:03.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.48,0:22:05.81,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,但完全没有赢了她的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:06.02,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}可你的脸很红哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.89,0:22:07.92,Takagi san—Text,,0,0,0,,是你的错觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:24.69,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}もっと遊んで　指を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.77,0:22:27.64,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}呼んでいる声がするわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:34.27,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}本当も嘘も　興味がないのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.49,0:22:37.66,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}指先からすり抜けてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:40.64,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}欲張りな笑い声も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:47.36,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}ごちゃ混ぜにした　スープに溶かすから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:54.11,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}音に合わせて　靴をならして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:22:59.32,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}あたしだけの秘密の場所
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:07.34,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}走る雲の影を飛び越えるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.66,0:23:13.11,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}夏の匂い追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.38,0:23:19.59,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}あぁ夢はいつまでも覚めない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.86,0:23:25.08,Takagi san—Ed-Japanese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}歌う風のように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:24.69,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}再多玩玩  打个响指
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.77,0:22:27.64,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}听到了你的呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:34.27,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}无论是真是假  我都不感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.49,0:22:37.66,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}指尖悄然滑过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:40.64,Takagi san—Ed-Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}畅怀发出的笑声
